# UI — shadcn + Tailwind

- **Design tokens**: stay on **neutral** + **CSS variables** from [globals.css](../../src/app/globals.css). Extend tokens there instead of scattered hex values.
- **Components**: [components.json](../../components.json) — style `base-nova`, shadcn/ui under `src/components/ui/`. Import via `@/components/ui/*` and `@/lib/utils` (`cn`).
- **New primitives**: add with shadcn CLI — see [.cursor/skills/add-shadcn-component/SKILL.md](../skills/add-shadcn-component/SKILL.md).
- **UX**: consistent spacing (`gap-*`, `p-*`), visible focus, loading/disabled on buttons and form submits, associate labels (see auth forms under `src/app/(auth)/`).
- **Motion**: `motion` is available — use sparingly; prefer simple CSS transitions for hovers. Do not animate layout-affecting properties in ways that hurt CLS.
